mqvpn (0.3.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add FEC (Forward Error Correction) and packet reinjection support.
  * Add support for all xquic schedulers and congestion control settings.
  * Add cipher suite configuration options.
  * Add user authentication support (username in addition to pre-shared key).
  * Add path rotation on startup.
  * Add ICMP handling support.
  * Backup mode: use xquic standby API for schedulers that support it.
  * Add routes management options (--gateway, --no-gateway).
  * Refactor tick() and client_new() into focused helper functions.
  * Fix memory leaks in client teardown path.
  * Fix multipath route detection errors.
  * Merge main: CMakeLists.txt now includes icmp.c.

 -- mqvpn maintainers <maintainers@example.com>  Sat, 25 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000

mqvpn (0.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging.
  * Add backup/failover path support (--backup-path).
  * Add TCP control API for runtime user and path management.

 -- mqvpn maintainers <maintainers@example.com>  Fri, 27 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000
